          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
              <h5 class="mb-0">Frequently asked questions</h5>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body bg-light">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                  <h5 class="fs-0">How does <%= appInfo.app_name %> 's pricing work?</h5>
                  <p class="fs--1">
                    <%= appInfo.app_name %> offers three pricing options for its services.
                      Firstly, there is a free plan with a cost of $0, providing
                      basic features. Secondly, the monthly plan costs $8 per
                      month, granting access to additional functionalities on a
                      month-to-month basis. Lastly, users can opt for the annually
                      plan at a cost of $60, providing a cost-effective solution
                      for those who commit to a year-long subscription. Customers
                      can choose the plan that best suits their needs and budget,
                      making <%= appInfo.app_name %> a flexible and affordable choice for
                        various users.
                  </p>
                  <h5 class="fs-0">What forms of payment do you accept?</h5>
                  <p class="fs--1">
                    We accept PayPal, Apple Pay, Google pay and Debit Card. As
                    we continuously grow, we may explore other leading payment
                    methods in the future.
                  </p>
                  <h5 class="fs-0">
                    Can i transfer my subscription to another account?
                  </h5>
                  <p class="fs--1">
                    Yes, you may be able to transfer your subscription to
                    another account. However, this option is available only in
                    specific cases, and eligibility criteria may apply. Contact
                    customer support for assistance.
                  </p>
                  <h5 class="fs-0">How secure is <%= appInfo.app_name %> ?</h5>
                  <p class="fs--1 mb-lg-0">
                    <%= appInfo.app_name %> 's security is robust and reliable. It employs
                      advanced encryption protocols to safeguard data transmission
                      and storage, protecting against unauthorized access. Regular
                      security audits and updates ensure that vulnerabilities are
                      promptly addressed. Multi-factor authentication enhances
                      user access controls, bolstering overall security. The
                      platform's proactive monitoring and dedicated security team
                      further reinforce its defense against potential threats.
                      With these measures in place, <%= appInfo.app_name %> offers a highly
                        secure environment for users to share and collaborate with
                        confidence.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                  <h5 class="fs-0">Will I be charged sales tax?</h5>
                  <p class="fs--1">
                    Sales tax depends on the country. Some countries apply sales
                    tax to purchases, while others may not. Check your country's
                    tax laws to determine if you'll be charged sales tax.
                  </p>
                  <h5 class="fs-0">Do you offer discounts?</h5>
                  <p class="fs--1">
                    Yes, we offer discounts periodically, including during
                    special events and holidays.
                  </p>
                  <h5 class="fs-0">Do you offer academic pricing?</h5>
                  <p class="fs--1">
                    We're happy to work with student groups using <%= appInfo.app_name %> .
                      Contact Us
                  </p>
                  <h5 class="fs-0">
                    Is there an on-premise version of <%= appInfo.app_name %> ?
                  </h5>
                  <p class="fs--1">
                    We are passionate about the web. We don't plan to offer an
                    internally hosted version of <%= appInfo.app_name %> . We hope you trust
                      us to provide a robust and secure service so you can do the
                      work only your team can do.
                  </p>
                  <h5 class="fs-0">What is your refund policy?</h5>
                  <p class="fs--1">
                    We do not offer refunds apart from exceptions listed below.
                    If you cancel your plan before the next renewal cycle, you
                    will retain access to paid features until the end of your
                    subscription period. When your subscription expires, you
                    will lose access to paid features and all data associated
                    with those features.
                  </p>
                  <h5 class="fs-0">
                    What is the highest that anyone have earned on this
                    platform?
                  </h5>
                  <p class="fs--1 mb-0">
                    There is literaly no limit and you can earn as much as you
                    like. We do not leak what the earning of our users.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          
            <!-- Ask your question form -->
            <div class="card-footer py-3">
              <div class="text-center py-3">
                <h6 class="fs-0 font-weight-normal">Have more questions?</h6>
                <a class="btn btn-falcon-primary btn-sm" href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#exampleModal">Ask us
                  anything</a>
              </div>
              <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel"
                aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
                  <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header bg-light">
                      <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">
                        Ask your question
                      </h5>
                      <button class="close" type="button" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                        <span class="font-weight-light" aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                      </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                      <form>
                        <div class="form-group">
                          <label for="name">Name</label>
                          <input class="form-control" id="name" type="text" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                          <label for="emailModal">Email</label>
                          <input class="form-control" id="emailModal" type="email" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                          <label for="question">Question</label>
                          <textarea class="form-control" id="question" rows="4"></textarea>
                        </div>
                      </form>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-footer bg-light rounded">
                      <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" type="button" data-dismiss="modal">
                        Close
                      </button>
                      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" type="submit">
                        Send
                      </button>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <footer><%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %></footer>
        </div>
      </div>
